{
  "texts": [
    "Most AI companies have an overarching research agenda (e.g.",
    "Google DeepMind's early bet on reinforcement learning [158] or Anthropic's focus on empirical safety research [9]).",
    "This agenda influences what projects the company works on.",
    "The ethics board could try to influence that agenda.",
    "It could advocate for increasing focus on safety and alignment research [4,72,116]."
  ]
}